'''史蒂芬·巴塞特'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Bassett}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]說客，「範式研究小組」（PRG）的創始人和現任執行董事，力圖遊說[[美國政府|美國政府]]承認存在[[外星生命|外星生命]]並解密相關資訊。<ref>{{Cite web|title=For UFO lobbyist, truth is out there|url=https://www.politico.com/story/2010/07/for-ufo-lobbyist-truth-is-out-there-039383|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=|date=2010-07-06|last=Lovley|first=Erika|publisher=POLITICO|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203174707/https://www.politico.com/story/2010/07/for-ufo-lobbyist-truth-is-out-there-039383|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
巴塞特擁有{{le|埃克德學院|Eckerd College}}的[[物理學|物理學]]學位<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Stars Not Likely to Align for Unidentified Candidate Running on UFO Platform|url=https://cnsmaryland.org/2002/11/01/stars-not-likely-to-align-for-unidentified-candidate-running-on-ufo-platform/|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2002-11-01|publisher=Capital News Service|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203004028/https://cnsmaryland.org/2002/11/01/stars-not-likely-to-align-for-unidentified-candidate-running-on-ufo-platform/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1996年，巴塞特成為一名註冊說客，並移居[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]，成立了「範式研究小組」（Paradigm Research Group，縮寫：PRG）<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFO Lobbyists Are Trying to Get the Truth From Congress, and They're Winning|url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/gyz8x3/there-are-ufo-lobbyists-in-dc-and-lawmakers-are-apparently-listening|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2019-10-05|publisher=VICE|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224063141/https://www.vice.com/en/article/gyz8x3/there-are-ufo-lobbyists-in-dc-and-lawmakers-are-apparently-listening|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet the Lobbyist Pressuring the US Gov’t to Disclose Extraterrestrial Activity|url=https://observer.com/2015/09/meet-the-lobbyist-pressuring-the-us-government-to-disclose-extraterrestrial-activity/|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2015-09-16|work=Observer|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208064615/https://observer.com/2015/09/meet-the-lobbyist-pressuring-the-us-government-to-disclose-extraterrestrial-activity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年7月13日，成立了「地外現象政治行動委員會」（Extraterrestrial Phenomena Political Action Committee）<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Making of an Exopolitical Activist|url=https://paradigmresearchgroup.org/bio/|accessdate=2021-01-29|publisher=Paradigm Research Group|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203012612/https://paradigmresearchgroup.org/bio/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴塞特被媒體稱為是美國唯一有關[[不明飛行物|不明飛行物]]/外星生命議題的註冊說客<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why UFO activists are excited about another Clinton presidency|url=https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2015/04/hillary-clinton-ufo-aliens-podesta/|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2015-04-03|last=Vicens|first=A. J.|publisher=Mother Jones|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203041113/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2015/04/hillary-clinton-ufo-aliens-podesta/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Could Vladimir Putin reveal aliens exist? Kremlin chief asked to lift 'truth embargo'|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/811855/Vladimir-Putin-aliens-exist-Steve-Bassett-Paridigm-Research-Group-Russia-UFO|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2017-06-01|last=Austin|first=Jon|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208033830/https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/811855/Vladimir-Putin-aliens-exist-Steve-Bassett-Paridigm-Research-Group-Russia-UFO|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=EXCLUSIVE: Barack Obama 'on brink of revealing intelligent aliens visit Earth'|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/672284/EXCLUSIVE-Barack-Obama-on-brink-of-revealing-intelligent-aliens-visit-Earth|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2016-05-20|last=Austin|first=Jon|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227080432/https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/672284/EXCLUSIVE-Barack-Obama-on-brink-of-revealing-intelligent-aliens-visit-Earth|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Will Cameron reveal truth about aliens? Rare footage shows UK PM vow to open UFO files|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/676843/Will-Cameron-reveal-truth-about-aliens-Rare-footage-shows-UK-PM-vow-to-open-UFO-files|accessdate=2021-01-29|date=2016-06-04|last=Austin|first=Jon|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201195253/https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/676843/Will-Cameron-reveal-truth-about-aliens-Rare-footage-shows-UK-PM-vow-to-open-UFO-files|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

曾擔任前[[鳳凰城|鳳凰城]]市議員[[法蘭西絲·艾瑪·巴伍德|法蘭西絲·艾瑪·巴伍德]]1998年競選{{le|亞利桑那州州務卿|Secretary of State of Arizona}}的競選主任<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1998-jan-25-mn-11903-story.html|title=Arizona Political Race One for the ‘X-Files’|work=Los Angeles Times|date=1998-01-25|accessdate=2021-08-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804145140/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1998-jan-25-mn-11903-story.html|archivedate=2021-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2002年，巴塞特以[[獨立人士|獨立人士]]身分參選{{link-en|馬里蘭州第八國會選區|Maryland's 8th congressional district}}的[[聯邦眾議員|眾議員]]席位，雖然他成功徵集了超過五千個聯署簽名、獲得登上選票的資格，但被[[民調|民調]]所忽略，也未能參與辯論<ref name=":0" />。

2013年，範式研究小組在華盛頓特區舉辦了名為「{{link-ja|公民揭秘聽證會|シチズンズ・ヒアリング・ディスクロージャー公聴会}}」的模擬聽證會，以每人2万美元的酬勞邀请了6位美国前议员參與。包括[[斯坦頓·弗里德曼|斯坦頓·弗里德曼]]在內的來自世界各地的UFO研究者在該次聽證會上作證<ref>{{cite news|author1=韩莎莎|title=美国组织花钱请前议员证明政府隐瞒与外星人接触|url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJAjVg|accessdate=2021-01-29|agency=人民網|publisher=環球網|date=2013-05-01|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203151526/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJAjVg|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Former members of Congress hold weird faux UFO hearing in Washington, after the price is right|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/ex-u-s-reps-hold-faux-ufo-hearing-price-article-1.1331805|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=|date=|last=Friedman|first=Dan|publisher=New York Daily News|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208153523/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/ex-u-s-reps-hold-faux-ufo-hearing-price-article-1.1331805|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

